{"tid":1072342,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows Defender 移植 MacOS 提供保安功能","createTime":"2019-03-22T03:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T11:58:41.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de8978065d4e97e3822cd272cc1da516572d5dab","tid":1072342,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"Microsoft 自從 Windows XP 開始，就有推出自家防毒軟件 Windows Defender，到了 Windows 10 更是完全整合在系統之中，提供保安功能。最近 Microsoft 就把這個軟件移植到 macOS 上，提供類似的功能，不過暫時只向企業客戶提供。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Screenshot-2019-03-22-at-12.00.39-AM-1200x633.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FScreenshot-2019-03-22-at-12.00.39-AM-1200x633.png&h=97fe6f74&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n今次推出的移植版 Windows Defender 因為已經不是在 Windows 上運作，因此改稱為 Microsoft Defender Threat Protection。這是繼 Microsoft 推出 Windows Defender 的 Chrome 和 Firefox 瀏覽器插件後，再一次在其他平台上移植這防毒軟件。其功能與 Windows 版本類似，提供全面的病毒和威脅保護，亦可以進行快速或完全病毒掃描等。<br />\n<br />\n不過這個工具目前只提供予企業客戶，方便他們在同時有 Windows 和 Mac 電腦的企業環境中管理電腦的安全保護。工具會透過 Microsoft 本身的 AutoUpdate 自動更新，目前未知 Microsoft 會否把它推出予一般用家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/security/blog/2019/03/21/microsoft-defender-atp-for-mac-new-threat-and-vulnerability-management-capabilities/?ranMID=24542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fsecurity%2Fblog%2F2019%2F03%2F21%2Fmicrosoft-defender-atp-for-mac-new-threat-and-vulnerability-management-capabilities%2F%3FranMID%3D24542&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroExZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=9a60ceff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/security/blog/2019/03/21/microsoft-defender-atp-for-mac-new-threat-and-vulnerability-management-capabilities/?ranMID=24542</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/22/microsoft-defender-atp-for-mac/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F22%2Fmicrosoft-defender-atp-for-mac%2Fsoftware%2F&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroExZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=429362fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/22/microsoft-defender-atp-for-mac/software/</a>"},{"pid":"f9d794790153b73ec73b483d788fe3765f1050fa","tid":1072342,"uid":115189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"Windows 嘅全部都煩到嘔<br />\n<br />\n喺Windows 成日逼你更新，彈出彈入<br />\n<br />\n到Mac用Office 又成日叫你更新，次次都要閂嘅啲office software等佢裝完先開翻<br />\n<br />\n而家搞埋個Defender 實噪到仆街<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft = 維園廢老"},{"pid":"e1ac2604a04562376bdd558ed9a2a390251e9b73","tid":1072342,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d794790153b73ec73b483d788fe3765f1050fa","tid":1072342,"uid":115189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"Windows 嘅全部都煩到嘔<br />\n<br />\n喺Windows 成日逼你更新，彈出彈入<br />\n<br />\n到Mac用Office 又成日叫你更新，次次都要閂嘅啲office software等佢裝完先開翻<br />\n<br />\n而家搞埋個Defender 實噪到仆街<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft = 維園廢老"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"又要用又要屌"},{"pid":"5b6026648c554b2396234c1d0c32fa3c56c3a025","tid":1072342,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ac2604a04562376bdd558ed9a2a390251e9b73","tid":1072342,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d794790153b73ec73b483d788fe3765f1050fa","tid":1072342,"uid":115189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"Windows 嘅全部都煩到嘔<br />\n<br />\n喺Windows 成日逼你更新，彈出彈入<br />\n<br />\n到Mac用Office 又成日叫你更新，次次都要閂嘅啲office software等佢裝完先開翻<br />\n<br />\n而家搞埋個Defender 實噪到仆街<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft = 維園廢老"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"又要用又要屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"有得唔用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acfcda608cf066b4cf1675e95f07b93a206f875","tid":1072342,"uid"